summary: Experienced communications & marketing manager in both public and private worlds. Inspired by the power of engaging campaigns, community, memorable experiences, art and culture. Skilled in strategy development, business planning, campaign building, copyediting, social media marketing, relationship building and communication strategy development. A Dalhousie and Maastricht University graduate and former student-athlete who is creative at heart. Currently focused on Brand and Positioning at Deloitte Canada.
